'''Tolkien Calendar 1994''' was published by the [[Finnish Tolkien Society]]. The calendar features pen and ink illustrations by [[Mikko Raunonpoika Juhola]], [[Jukka-Petteri Halme]], and [[Petri Hiltunen]].

* Dimensions: 11 3/4 x 8 1/4 inches
* Stapled on the fold
